_sText:
A quick map I made after getting the custom toon textures to see how they would come out. 
Its a Fun map, although bots act a little strange on it. The map has 20 spawns on each side so it can handle a bunch of people. 

Special Thanks to TomGreen For getting me back into mapping.

---------------------------

You do not need to download any custom textures to get this to work, they are included in the bsp.

---------------------------

To install place the .bsp file and the .nav file in cstrike/maps
